<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c1">" الْكَشْفُ عَنْ مُجَاوَزَةِ هَذِهِ الأُمَّةِ الأَلْفِ "</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٧٧ - النَّبِيُّ وَصَاحِبَاهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هُوَ مَثَلٌ يُضْرَبُ لِلتَّعَاضُدِ لَا حَدِيثَ وَلا أَثَرَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥٧٨ - النِّسَاءُ يَنْصُرُ بَعْضُهُنَّ بَعْضًا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قَالَهُ عِكْرِمَةُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥٧٩ - النِّسْيَانُ طَبْعُ الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ بِهَذَا لَكِنْ فِي الْحَدِيثِ <span class="c1">" الْمُؤْمِنُ نَسَّاءٌ إِذَا ذُكِّرَ تذكر "</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>